Package: inbox-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: mail
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10)
Maintainer: Peak Services Inc. <support@peakservices-inc.com>
Description: InboxAgent - Privacy-first local AI email organization agent
 InboxAgent is a desktop application that automatically organizes
 your email using configurable rules and optional local AI classification
 via Ollama. It runs entirely on your machine for maximum privacy.
